<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - Not Found</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #343a40;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .error-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .emoji {
      font-size: 5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .search-box {
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      width: 80%;
      border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <div class="emoji">üîç</div>
    <h1>404 - Page Not Found</h1>
    <p>The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.</p>
    <input type="text" class="search-box" placeholder="Search our site...">
    <p><a href="/">‚Üê Return to Home</a> or try searching above.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>